title: Alaska Structures Provides 365 Medium Shelters to USAF
text:
Alaska Structures Inc.
ANCHORAGE, Alaska , Oct. 16, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Alaska Structures Â® recently completed a contract for 365 new and improved U.S. Air Force Medium Shelter Systems.
The contract, valued at more than $15 million , was finished on time and on budget, continuing Alaska Structures' standing as the USAF shelter supplier of choice.
Since 1999, Alaska Structures has provided more than 35,000 American-made military shelters and over 16,000 Environmental Control Units (ECU) to U.S. and Coalition Forces for operations around the world.
